# Data

This folder is intentionally left empty.

Download the NASA CMAPSS dataset from either source below
and place the extracted .txt files here:

- NASA PCoE: https://www.nasa.gov/intelligent-systems-division/discovery-and-systems-health/pcoe/pcoe-data-set-repository/
- Kaggle mirror: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/behrad3d/nasa-cmaps

Expected files:
  train_FD001.txt  train_FD002.txt  train_FD003.txt  train_FD004.txt
  test_FD001.txt   test_FD002.txt   test_FD003.txt   test_FD004.txt
  RUL_FD001.txt    RUL_FD002.txt    RUL_FD003.txt    RUL_FD004.txt
